---
const footerLinks = [
  { label: "FAQ", href: "/faq/" },
  { label: "Tarifs", href: "/tarifs/" },
  { label: "Presse", href: "/presse/" },
  { label: "Actualites", href: "/actualites/" },
  { label: "Contact", href: "/contact/" },
  { label: "CGV", href: "/conditions-generales-de-vente-et-dutilisation-des-jeux/" },
];
---

<footer class="bg-tac-dark-blue">
  <!-- Top separator -->
  <hr class="border-t-2 border-tac-orange mx-5" />

  <!-- Main footer -->
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-5 py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-10">

      <!-- Col 1: Address -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-mulish font-semibold text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          33 Port Saint-Sauveur<br />
          31000 Toulouse
        </p>
        <a href="tel:0534594581" class="flex items-center gap-3 text-tac-orange font-mulish font-semibold text-sm hover:no-underline">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
          </svg>
          05 34 59 45 81
        </a>
        <!-- Social icons -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-6">
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/tactisens" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white/30 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-tac-orange hover:border-tac-orange transition-all" aria-label="Facebook">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18.77,7.46H14.5v-1.9c0-.9.6-1.1,1-1.1h3V.5h-4.33C10.24.5,9.5,3.44,9.5,5.32v2.15h-3v4h3v12h5v-12h3.85l.42-4Z"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/tactisens" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white/30 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-tac-orange hover:border-tac-orange transition-all" aria-label="Instagram">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12,2.16c3.2,0,3.58.01,4.85.07,3.25.15,4.77,1.69,4.92,4.92.06,1.27.07,1.65.07,4.85s-.01,3.58-.07,4.85c-.15,3.23-1.66,4.77-4.92,4.92-1.27.06-1.65.07-4.85.07s-3.58-.01-4.85-.07c-3.26-.15-4.77-1.7-4.92-4.92-.06-1.27-.07-1.65-.07-4.85s.01-3.58.07-4.85C2.38,3.92,3.9,2.38,7.15,2.23,8.42,2.17,8.8,2.16,12,2.16ZM12,0C8.74,0,8.33.01,7.05.07,2.7.27.27,2.7.07,7.05.01,8.33,0,8.74,0,12s.01,3.67.07,4.95c.2,4.36,2.62,6.78,6.98,6.98C8.33,23.99,8.74,24,12,24s3.67-.01,4.95-.07c4.35-.2,6.78-2.62,6.98-6.98C23.99,15.67,24,15.26,24,12s-.01-3.67-.07-4.95c-.2-4.35-2.62-6.78-6.98-6.98C15.67.01,15.26,0,12,0Zm0,5.84A6.16,6.16,0,1,0,18.16,12,6.16,6.16,0,0,0,12,5.84ZM12,16a4,4,0,1,1,4-4A4,4,0,0,1,12,16ZM18.41,4.15a1.44,1.44,0,1,0,1.44,1.44A1.44,1.44,0,0,0,18.41,4.15Z"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g187175-d15008937-Reviews-Tactisens-Toulouse_Haute_Garonne_Occitanie.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white/30 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-tac-orange hover:border-tac-orange transition-all" aria-label="TripAdvisor">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12.006 4.295c-2.67 0-5.338.784-7.645 2.353H0l1.963 2.135a5.997 5.997 0 004.04 10.43 5.976 5.976 0 004.075-1.6L12.006 19.7l1.928-2.088a5.976 5.976 0 004.075 1.601 5.997 5.997 0 004.04-10.43L24 6.648h-4.35a13.573 13.573 0 00-7.644-2.353zM6.003 17.213a3.997 3.997 0 110-7.994 3.997 3.997 0 010 7.994zm11.994 0a3.997 3.997 0 110-7.994 3.997 3.997 0 010 7.994zM6.003 11.22a1.998 1.998 0 100 3.996 1.998 1.998 0 000-3.996zm11.994 0a1.998 1.998 0 100 3.996 1.998 1.998 0 000-3.996z"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Col 2: Links -->
      <div>
        <nav class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          {footerLinks.map((link) => (
            <a href={link.href} class="font-share font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-white hover:text-tac-orange hover:no-underline">
              {link.label}
            </a>
          ))}
        </nav>
      </div>

      <!-- Col 3: Accessibilite -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-tac-orange flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 2a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zM10.05 7.47C8.32 7.83 7 9.35 7 11.15v1.35c0 .55.45 1 1 1s1-.45 1-1v-1.35c0-.62.38-1.15.92-1.38L12 10.7l2.08-.93c.54.23.92.76.92 1.38v1.35c0 .55.45 1 1 1s1-.45 1-1v-1.35c0-1.8-1.32-3.32-3.05-3.68L12 7l-1.95.47zM8.5 15c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1v4c0 .55.45 1 1 1s1-.45 1-1v-4c0-.55-.45-1-1-1zm7 0c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1v4c0 .55.45 1 1 1s1-.45 1-1v-4c0-.55-.45-1-1-1z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="font-share font-bold text-tac-orange uppercase text-lg tracking-wide">Accessibilite</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="font-mulish font-semibold text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/90">
          L'espace d'accueil et les Escape Room de Tactisens Escape Game Toulouse sont accessibles aux PMR (Personnes a Mobilite Reduite) et autres situations de handicap. Pour plus de details, consultez notre FAQ.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Col 4: Securite -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-tac-orange flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
          <h3 class="font-share font-bold text-tac-orange uppercase text-lg tracking-wide">Securite</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="font-mulish font-semibold text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/90">
          Afin de proposer des Escape Game surs, Tactisens Escape Game Toulouse a eu toutes les autorisations de la Direction de la Securite Civile et des Risques Majeurs. Un Escape Game pour jouer en securite.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom bar -->
  <div class="border-t border-white/10 py-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-tac-orange text-sm font-mulish font-semibold mb-2">
      <a href="/mentions-legales/" class="hover:underline">Mentions legales</a>
      <span class="mx-1">&ndash;</span>
      <a href="/politique-de-cookies/" class="hover:underline">Politique de confidentialite</a>
      <span class="mx-1">&ndash;</span>
      <a href="#" class="hover:underline">Gestion des cookies</a>
    </p>
    <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">&copy; Tactisens 2025</p>
  </div>
</footer>
